#Registration
#
**Sign up**  curl -H "Content-Type: application/json"   -X POST -d '{"email":"ievgen.paliichuk@gmail.com","url":"crm.com"}' --include http://localhost:9000/signup

**Activate user**  curl -H "Content-Type: application/json" -X POST -d '{"token":"lv4lfro7amjepk3p4arfcaoed56akju93pju80i3ikrr","email":"ievgen.paliichuk@gmail.com","password":"123456","companyName":"curlCompany","vatId":"curlVat","contactProfile":{"firstname":"curlFristName","lastname":"curlLastName","email":"curl@curl.com","address":"curlAddresss","city":"curlCity","zipCode":"curlZip","phoneNumberMobile":"curlNum","phoneNumberHome":"culrNum","phoneNumberWork":"curlNum"}}' --include http://localhost:9000/activate-user

**Login**  curl -H "Content-Type: application/json"   -X POST -d '{"username":"ievgen.paliichuk@gmail.com","password":"123456"}' --include http://localhost:9000/login 


